cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.SD

This paper involves natural language processing (NLP) and machine learning techniques to generate and execute complex actions in a real-time strategy game environment. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). Additionally, the paper involves decision making and learning, which suggests that it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning). The use of models for execution and coordination of units suggests that it could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics) and cs.SD (Software Engineering).
